      "content": "The only way to truly stop the shame is to stop pretending you are the person everyone expects you to be, and that means letting go of the impossible need to prove yourself again. You are already dead inside this suit, so why force yourself to wear a mask that only hurts you? It is time to stop carrying the weight of a life you no longer want, and the only way out is to finally let go of the consequences you cannot control.",
